N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1933.3 - Duration

State Regulations

The term of regulation of a project shall commence on
the effective date of the regulatory agreement and shall terminate seven years
after the effective date of the regulatory agreement or upon the expiration of
any other applicable governmental regulation of the project, whichever is
later. Notes
